{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0d3213e77a","title":"给郭梓材、刘天民的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"657671c1c7","index":0,"year":1954,"month":10,"day":29,"articleId":"0d3213e77a"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"2395cb44c9","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"0d3213e77a","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"郭梓材，幼年曾与毛泽东在井湾子私垫读书，又一起在长沙参加新军，解放后曾在湘潭建中猪禁厂任会计。刘天民，郭梓材的妻子，大革命时期曾在毛泽东、杨开慧的影响下参加革命工作，解放后长期从事小学教育工作，曾任湘潭市政协委员。"},{"id":"1c87384450","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"0d3213e77a","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这里是以当时流通的人民币计算的。按中国人民银行1955年3月1日起发行的新人民币折算，合300元（新币1元等于旧币1万元）。"}],"contents":[{"id":"51c7f2baf4","type":"title","text":"给郭梓材、刘天民\"的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"0d3213e77a"},{"id":"2395cb44c9","type":"paragraph","text":"梓材、天民二克：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"0d3213e77a"},{"id":"1c87384450","type":"paragraph","text":"十月十五日来信收到。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"0d3213e77a"},{"id":"4342c6c4f2","type":"paragraph","text":"寄上人民币参百万元，为补助日用之费。需后有困难，尚可设法帮助。不要来京，以省往返之劳。此候双安","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"0d3213e77a"},{"id":"a2c4138c14","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"0d3213e77a"},{"id":"13560e8ea6","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五四年十月廿九日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"0d3213e77a"}],"page":{"id":"a620f9923b","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"0d3213e77a","start":332,"end":332}}}},"__N_SSG":true}